sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser (SPA)
    participant Django as Django Backend
    participant IdP as IdP (Entra ID)

    Note over Browser,IdP: Pure Django SAML - Django acts as SAML Service Provider

    Browser->>Django: GET /api/auth/discovery?email=user@example.com
    Django-->>Browser: 302 to IdP SSO URL

    Browser->>IdP: GET (SAML AuthnRequest redirect)
    Note over IdP: User authenticates
    IdP-->>Browser: HTML form auto-post with SAMLResponse

    Browser->>Django: POST /api/auth/saml/acs/
    Note over Django: Validate assertion signature (X.509 cert)<br/>Extract email - create or find user<br/>Store short-lived hyver_token (TTL ~60s)
    Django-->>Browser: 302 to /callback
    Note over Browser: Cookie received: hyver_token (HttpOnly - Secure - Max-Age=60)

    Browser->>Django: GET /api/auth/token/
    Note over Django: Look up and consume hyver_token<br/>Return long-lived DRF access token
    Django-->>Browser: 200 {"token":"...","email":"user@example.com"}

    Note over Browser: Login complete - DRF token stored
